    <text>
        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>Baltimore</placeName>
                <date>September 28<hi rend="sup">th</hi> 1832</date>
            </p>
            <p>Dear <addressee>Isaac</addressee></p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">I recd your last, nothing new I have to acquaint<lb/> you with but
                that we are all thank god <sic>wery</sic> well the cholera<lb/> has decreased that I
                hope there is no more Danger to be apprehended<lb/> from it yet we are obliged to be
                very <sic>carefull</sic> in our Dist. I hope<lb/> you are Quite well and may the god
                of our Fathers write you in the<lb/> Book of Life Health and <sic>Hapiness</sic>,
                    <persName>Manuel Judah</persName> arrived here yesterday<lb/> Quite well as soon
                as you hear from your Brother, let me know it<lb/> your aunt and all the
                    <sic>familia</sic> send <sic>there</sic> Love and wish you a<lb/> Happy new year
                remember us all kindly to our friends the <persName>Peixottos</persName><lb/>
                wishing them a Happy new year and many more to come pray dear<lb/>
                <persName>Isaac</persName> do not exert your self too much in reading the prayers
                    <add>ר"ה</add><lb/> take good care of your self I have nothing to add but
                Remain</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">your friends <persName role="author">Zalma Rehine</persName></p>
            <p>remember me to <persName>Mr Allen</persName> &amp; <sic>familia</sic>
                <persName>Mr Levy</persName> and <persName>Mrs Cohens</persName><lb/>
                <sic>familia</sic> and all friends in your Place</p>
            <pb n="4"/>
            <p>
                <addressee>Mr Isaac Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p>to the care of <persName>A C Peixotto Esqr</persName></p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
            </p>
        </body>
